snippet.title: International Space Banana - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1331670/International_Space_Banana/

Take control of an astronaut, turned banana... Spin, bounce and STRUGGLE as you attempt to navigate through levels that are simply out-of-this-world; on your own, or with friends in multiplayer mode! 

Remember, in space nobody can hear you rage :)
